# ---- POLYREPO SPLIT — apps/ MIGRATED TO SEPARATE REPOS ----
# apps/ is excluded from abyss-core. Each app lives in its own repo.
# See .agent/ARCHITECTURE.md §8 for the polyrepo plan.
apps/

# ---- EXPLICIT EXEMPTIONS (TRACKED BY DESIGN) ----
# Load-bearing negations — DO NOT REMOVE.
# Git evaluates .gitignore top-down; trailing negations override earlier rules.
# KEPT: .agent/ (multi-agent coordination memory) + CLAUDE.md (Claude Code project instructions)
!.agent/
!.agent/**
!pnpm-lock.yaml
